FlipUOnly: Flips U only on all particles.
FlipVOnly: Flips V only on all particles.
RandomFlipUV: Flips UV randomly for each particle on spawn.
RandomFlipUOnly: Flips U only randomly for each particle on spawn.
RandomFlipVOnly: Flips V only randomly for each particle on spawn.
RandomFlipUVIndependent: Flips U and V independently at random for each particle on spawn.
